folios.text:
28 ꝛ Sum lund ze
maꝛtꝛenbvrg
Sumut pope ꝑꝛo̊
Sicving hůtzan
ꝑꝛeꝛ ꝑ̅m̅ ꝑanꝑůꝛ ꝑriůꝛ

Vo̊ luttꝛingea
Jotef ꝑon ꝑarꝛlunt ꝑriůꝛ
Bolꝰawin ꝑo minꝛeꝛt ꝑriůꝛ
Colin ꝑon bayan ꝑm̅ Bůneꝛt

Vo̊ holtan lant
Jotef ꝑo̊tlaꝛ
Hanꝛ ꝑrůtteꝰ
Hainricꝰ lant
ꝑan ꝑrůtburg
Hanꝛ ꝑon bencꝰelt ꝑm̅ ꝑriůꝛ
ꝑan joganꝫ ꝑrꝛn̛ꝫ
